<event name="STORAGE_CHECK_AUG_FR_LIVING_SHIP">
	<text>You ponder which crew would benefit the ship the most. [Higher-tier upgrades will replace earlier tiers.]:</text>
		<choice req="FR_LIST_HUMAN_SACRIFICE_0" max_group="0" blue="false" hidden="true">
			<text>Feed it a Human. [0/2] 
			[Next bonus: Your crew will gain +25% hazard resistance.]</text>
			<event>
			<text>The process is over in a matter of seconds. You can only hope it was painless.</text>
							<hiddenAug>FR_HUMAN_SACRIFICE_1</hiddenAug>
					<removeCrew class="LIST_CREW_HUMAN">
						<clone>false</clone>
						<text>Your crew cannot be cloned as the ship absorbed their soul as well.</text>
					</removeCrew>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>It is done.</text>
					<event/>
			</choice>
			</event>
		</choice>
