<event name="STORAGE_CHECK_AUG_FR_SUPREME_HATRED_LOAD">
	<loadEvent>STORAGE_CHECK_AUG_FR_SUPREME_HATRED</loadEvent>
</event>

<event name="STORAGE_CHECK_AUG_FR_SUPREME_HATRED">
	<text>Which buffs for you want to claim? All the possible bonuses are listed below.

Nexus Notoriety: All weapons gain +10 shield piercing.
General Notoriety: +25% chance to resist damage to your systems and hull.
Union Notoriety: Your crew clones and heals 100% faster.
Harmony Notoriety: Your ship gains Auto manning level 2 and Auto repair.
Ministry Notoriety: Gain a stackable 10 hit point energy shield.
Free Mantis Notoriety: All friendly crew gain the free mantis pheromone ability.
Outcast Notoriety: All friendly crew gain hazard immunity.
Imperial Notoriety: Every time your ship takes damage, 2 shards will break off and fly at your enemy which pierces 2 shields.
Gathering Notoriety: Nullifies the ammo cost of weapons.
Confederacy Notoriety: You will gain 10 scrap every jump (not affected by Scrap/Repair arms).
Geniocracy Notoriety: All enemy crew and drones on-board will lose 10hp/s.
Commonwealth Refuge Notoriety: Full ion immunity and boosts standard shield charge rate by 150%.
Argeonn Reputation: Cooldown between weapon shots is improved by 25 percent.
Syndicate Reputation: Adds an option during jumpspeed that gives 10 fleet delay and fully maps the upcoming sector.
Tiiikaka Reputation: Makes each crew only use half their usual crew space.</text>
	<choice hidden="true" req="FR_NEXUS_NOTORIETY" lvl="1" max_group="0">
		<text>Nexus bonus already claimed!
[All weapons gain +10 shield piercing.]</text>
		<event load="OPTION_INVALID"/>
    </choice>
	<choice req="FR_NEXUS_NOTORIETY_REQUIREMENT" lvl="1" max_group="0">
		<text>Claim the Nexus bonus.
[All weapons gain +10 shield piercing.]</text>
        <event>
            <text>The sins paid off. The bonus has been internalized.</text>
			<hiddenAug>FR_NEXUS_NOTORIETY</hiddenAug>
            <choice hidden="true">
                <text>Continue...</text>
                <event load="STORAGE_CHECK_AUG_FR_SUPREME_HATRED_LOAD"/>
            </choice>
        </event>
    </choice>
