		[Bonus: Enemy Hive Mantis are unable to fight.]</text>
		<event>
			<text>The process is over in a matter of seconds. You can only hope it was painless.</text>
				<hiddenAug>FR_SOUL_MANTIS_QUEEN</hiddenAug>
				<removeCrew class="fr_unique_mantis_queen">
					<clone>false</clone>
					<text>Your crew cannot be cloned as the ship absorbed their soul as well.</text>
				</removeCrew>
				<choice hidden="true">
					<text>It is done.</text>
						<event/>
				</choice>
		</event>
    </choice>
    <choice req="FR_SOUL_BEARD" lvl="1" max_group="41" blue="false" hidden="true">
        <text>Crew Fed: Purple Beard
		[Bonus Gained: Your crew gain the following Active Ability: Deploys a Stim Bomb in the room, buffing the movement speed, combat damage, sabotage damage, and repair speed by 20% for 10 seconds of himself and all friedly crew in the same room as them. The effect doesn't stack.]</text>
       	<event load="OPTION_INVALID"/>
    </choice>
    <choice req="FR_SOUL_STEALER_BEARD" lvl="1" max_group="41" blue="false" hidden="true">
		<text>Feed it Purple Beard
		[Bonus: Your crew gain the following Active Ability: Deploys a Stim Bomb in the room, buffing the movement speed, combat damage, sabotage damage, and repair speed by 20% for 10 seconds of himself and all friedly crew in the same room as them. The effect doesn't stack.]</text>
		<event>
			<text>The process is over in a matter of seconds. You can only hope it was painless.</text>
				<hiddenAug>FR_SOUL_BEARD</hiddenAug>
				<removeCrew class="fr_unique_purple_beard">
					<clone>false</clone>
					<text>Your crew cannot be cloned as the ship absorbed their soul as well.</text>
				</removeCrew>
				<choice hidden="true">
					<text>It is done.</text>
						<event/>
				</choice>
		</event>
    </choice>
	<choice>
		<text>Nevermind, do something else.</text>
		<event load="STORAGE_CHECK"/>
	</choice>
</event>

<!--
\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\
\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\
					COMBAT CHECK - THE ORACLE
\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\
\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\
-->	

<event name="FR_COMBAT_CHECK_THE_ORACLE">
	<text>What do you want to steal?</text>
	<choice req="fr_enemyHasWeapons" lvl="1" max_group="0" blue="false" hidden="true">
		<text>Weapon</text>
		<event>
			<text>The enemy weapon suddenly appears in your cargo.</text>
			<playSound>glitch</playSound>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Time for battle!</text>
					<event name="FR_COMBAT_CHECK_THE_ORACLE_WEAPON"/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
    <choice req="fr_enemyHasWeapons" lvl="0" max_lvl="0" max_group="0" blue="false" hidden="true">
        <text>The enemy has no weapons.</text>
       	<event load="OPTION_INVALID"/>
    </choice>
	<choice req="fr_enemyHasDrones" lvl="1" max_group="1" blue="false" hidden="true">
		<text>Drone</text>
		<event>
			<text>The enemy drone suddenly appears in your cargo.</text>
			<playSound>glitch</playSound>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Time for battle!</text>
					<event name="FR_COMBAT_CHECK_THE_ORACLE_DRONE"/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
    <choice req="fr_enemyHasDrones" lvl="0" max_lvl="0" max_group="1" blue="false" hidden="true">
        <text>The enemy has no drones.</text>
       	<event load="OPTION_INVALID"/>
    </choice>
	<choice req="fr_enemyHasCrew" lvl="1" max_group="2" blue="false" hidden="true">
		<text>Crew</text>
		<event>
			<text>The enemy crew suddenly appears in your ship, ready to fight for you.</text>
			<playSound>glitch</playSound>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Time for battle!</text>
					<event name="FR_COMBAT_CHECK_THE_ORACLE_CREW"/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
    <choice req="fr_enemyHasCrew" lvl="0" max_lvl="0" max_group="2" blue="false" hidden="true">
        <text>The enemy has no crew.</text>
       	<event load="OPTION_INVALID"/>
    </choice>
	<choice req="pilot" max_group="99" blue="false">
		<text>Do something else instead.</text>
		<event load="COMBAT_CHECK"/>
	</choice>
</event>


<!--
\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\
\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\
					COMBAT CHECK - CALLIE
\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\
\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\
-->	

<event name="FR_COMBAT_CHECK_EDUTAINMENT_MODULE">
	<text>Ready for an amazing adventure through the mathematical plane fields?</text>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Yes!</text>
		<event>
			<text>You wait for the module to fully load before activating its combat function. Time to get mathematical!</text>
			<triggeredEvent name="FR_EDUTAINMENT_TRIGGER" event="FR_EDUTAINMENT_QUESTIONS" seeded="false" loops="999999999" maxTime="15.0" minTime="15.0" thisFight="true" clearOnJump="true">
				<warningMessage id="fr_warning_math" x="444" y="46" time="5.0" r="0" g="255" b="0" centerText="true" flash="true" sound="surgeWarning" useWarningLine="true"/>
				<triggeredEventBox load="DEFAULT_TIMER">
					<warning flash="true" time="5.0"/>
					<tooltip>Your Math Question will occur after this countdown.</tooltip>
				</triggeredEventBox>
			</triggeredEvent>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice>
		<text>No...do something else instead.</text>
		<event load="COMBAT_CHECK"/>
	</choice>
</event>

<event name="FR_EDUTAINMENT_QUESTIONS">
	<loadEventList seeded="false" first="false" generate="false">
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_QUESTION_1"/>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_QUESTION_2"/>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_QUESTION_3"/>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_QUESTION_4"/>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_QUESTION_5"/>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_QUESTION_6"/>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_QUESTION_7"/>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_QUESTION_8"/>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_QUESTION_9"/>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_QUESTION_10"/>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_QUESTION_11"/>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_QUESTION_12"/>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_QUESTION_13"/>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_QUESTION_14"/>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_QUESTION_15"/>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_QUESTION_16"/>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_QUESTION_17"/>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_QUESTION_18"/>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_QUESTION_19"/>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_QUESTION_20"/>
	</loadEventList>
</event>

<event name="FR_EDUTAINMENT_QUESTION_WRONG">
	<text>Sorry Renegade, but it seems you got the question wrong. Bad students need to be punished.</text>
	<damage amount="3"/>
</event>
<event name="FR_EDUTAINMENT_QUESTION_CORRECT">
	<text>Excellent mathematical skills, Renegade! Now for your reward...</text>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Conitnue...</text>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_QUESTION_CORRECT_REWARDS"/>
	</choice>
</event>

<event name="FR_EDUTAINMENT_QUESTION_CORRECT_REWARDS">
	<loadEventList seeded="false" first="false" generate="false">
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_REWARD_FIRE"/>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_REWARD_FIRE"/>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_REWARD_FIRE"/>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_REWARD_BREACH"/>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_REWARD_BREACH"/>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_REWARD_BREACH"/>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_REWARD_SYSTEM_DAMAGE"/>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_REWARD_SYSTEM_DAMAGE"/>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_REWARD_HEAL"/>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_REWARD_HEAL"/>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_REWARD_SCRAP"/>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_REWARD_MISSILE"/>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_REWARD_DRONE"/>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_REWARD_FUEL"/>
	</loadEventList>
</event>

<event name="FR_EDUTAINMENT_REWARD_FIRE">
	<text>The enemy ship has been set on fire!</text>
	<enemyDamage amount="0" effect="fire" system="room"/>
	<enemyDamage amount="0" effect="fire" system="room"/>
</event>
<event name="FR_EDUTAINMENT_REWARD_BREACH">
	<text>The enemy ship is now full of holes!</text>
	<enemyDamage amount="0" effect="breach" system="random"/>
	<enemyDamage amount="0" effect="breach" system="random"/>
</event>
<event name="FR_EDUTAINMENT_REWARD_SYSTEM_DAMAGE">
	<text>The enemy ship's systems have been damaged!</text>
	<enemyDamage amount="1" system="random"/>
	<enemyDamage amount="1" system="random"/>
    <enemyDamage amount="-2"/>
</event>

<event name="FR_EDUTAINMENT_REWARD_HEAL">
	<text>Your ship is now back at top shape!</text>
	<damage amount="-99"/>
</event>

<event name="FR_EDUTAINMENT_REWARD_SCRAP">
	<text>You earned extra credits for such a great response!</text>
	<item_modify>
		<item min="5" max="10" type="scrap"/>
	</item_modify>
</event>

<event name="FR_EDUTAINMENT_REWARD_MISSILE">
	<text>Your armories have been resupplied!</text>
	<item_modify>
		<item min="1" max="3" type="missiles"/>
	</item_modify>
</event>

<event name="FR_EDUTAINMENT_REWARD_DRONE">
	<text>Your drone parts have been resupplied!</text>
	<item_modify>
		<item min="1" max="3" type="drones"/>
	</item_modify>
</event>

<event name="FR_EDUTAINMENT_REWARD_FUEL">
	<text>Your fuel reserves have been resupplied!</text>
	<item_modify>
		<item min="3" max="5" type="fuel"/>
	</item_modify>
</event>

<event name="FR_EDUTAINMENT_QUESTION_1">
	<text>For a brief moment Callie stops firing. "N-n-n-next problem! What is 6-3?"</text>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>9</text>
		<event load="FR_EDUTAINMENT_QUESTION_WRONG"/>
	</choice>
