	</mod-append:choice>
	<mod-append:choice blue="false" hidden="true" req="JUDGE_BOON_FR_LAVAMAN">
		<text>Currently active boon: Boon of Lava
		Your Lava crew will slowly damage enemies in the same room as them.</text>
